{"type":"message","id":"119e1d06","parentId":"78a21bd7","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:33:16.032Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The tool might have a different format or name. Let me try to run it using a slightly different approach - maybe the script is expecting a different format. Let me check how the script actually parses the arguments.","thinkingSignature":"38ecd6415fd814dd9ebb96bd6e8126b0264dc996b48db03154829396b9ce1542"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gbp1jnglkj48_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/qveris_tool.mjs","limit":100}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":8843,"output":95,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22922,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772591574904}}
{"type":"message","id":"3aa325c1","parentId":"119e1d06","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:33:16.039Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gbp1jnglkj48_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env node\n\nconst API_BASE = 'https://qveris.ai/api/v1';\nconst API_KEY = process.env.QVERIS_API_KEY;\n\nasync function search(query, limit = 10) {\n  const res = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/search`, {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': `Bearer ${API_KEY}`\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ query, limit })\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  return data;\n}\n\nasync function execute(toolId, params, searchId = null) {\n  const res = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/tools/execute`, {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': `Bearer ${API_KEY}`\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ tool_id: toolId, params, search_id: searchId })\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  return data;\n}\n\nasync function getByIds(...ids) {\n  const res = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/tools/get-by-ids`, {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': `Bearer ${API_KEY}`\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ ids })\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  return data;\n}\n\nconst cmd = process.argv[2];\nconst args = process.argv.slice(3);\n\nasync function main() {\n  try {\n    if (cmd === 'search') {\n      const query = args[0];\n      const limit = args.includes('--limit') ? parseInt(args[args.indexOf('--limit') + 1]) : 10;\n      const result = await search(query, limit);\n      console.log(JSON.stringify(result, null, 2));\n    } else if (cmd === 'execute') {\n      const toolId = args[0];\n      const searchIdIdx = args.indexOf('--search-id');\n      const searchId = searchIdIdx > -1 ? args[searchIdIdx + 1] : null;\n      const paramsIdx = args.indexOf('--params');\n      const params = paramsIdx > -1 ? JSON.parse(args[paramsIdx + 1]) : {};\n      const result = await execute(toolId, params, searchId);\n      console.log(JSON.stringify(result, null, 2));\n    } else if (cmd === 'get-by-ids') {\n      const result = await getByIds(...args.filter(a => !a.startsWith('--')));\n      console.log(JSON.stringify(result, null, 2));\n    } else {\n      console.error('Unknown command:', cmd);\n      process.exit(1);\n    }\n  } catch (err) {\n    console.error('Error:', err.message);\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n}\n\nmain();\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772591596038}}
{"type":"message","id":"a3eef0d2","parentId":"3aa325c1","timestamp":"2026-03-04T02:33:35.487Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue now. The script is parsing the command line args, and when I pass `--params '{\"codes\":\"...\"}'`, it needs to be parsed as JSON. But the issue is that the shell might be escaping it incorrectly.\n\nLet me try using a different approach - creating a temp JSON file with the params and passing that.","thinkingSignature":"cd022ee3f68afc5841e70b60a4790874209ba888d046d54e5330469def5fb791"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_syn3iicrhs0z_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && node -e \"\nconst API_BASE = 'https://qveris.ai/api/v1';\nconst API_KEY = process.env.QVERIS_API_KEY;\n\nasync function execute() {\n  const res = await fetch(\\`\\${API_BASE}/tools/execute\\`, {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': \\`Bearer \\${API_KEY}\\`\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ \n      tool_id: 'ths_ifind.real_time_quotation.v1', \n      params: { codes: '002149.SZ,601899.SH,601975.SH,000001.SH' },\n      search_id: null\n    })\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  console.log(JSON.stringify(data, null, 2));\n}\n\nexecute();\n\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":9546,"output":281,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23811,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772591596040}}
